info: Join us for the first of its kind 16 Day Python Session, enirely covered during after hours. No coding background is required. Take the opportunity and move from beginner to intermediate level in Python.
Join us to know more about Flutter and watch the keynotes/updates about Flutter. Also get coupons to access the best Flutter course co created with Google for free.
Explore ML is a series of ML related events which ranges from basic to advanced level. Join us for the first Explore ML event at MBCET.

Actions on Google is a platfom where you can you can build smart actions for google Assistant. Get ready to build some actions. We will also deal with building chat bots without writing even a single line of code. This session is not intended for first years.
DSC MBCET conducted this session to introduce Developer Student Clubs to the students. Around 20 students participated in the first event
